  "detailed_description": "\"Unlight:SchizoChronicle\" is a real time deck building game.<br />\r\nEvery turn each player purchases cards and fights against monsters.<br />\r\nIf you purchase a card, if that card gets added to your deck and you win the battle with the monster you get a \"sherd point\".<br />\r\nStrategically build and strengthen the deck and earn more \"shade points\" than other players!",
